originalText.text: Amazing Doctor who has compassion and professionalism which is hard to find. Dr Grover is a great listener and pays attention to detail with a calming and logical approach to healing. I'm surprised she is not in private practice but that doesn't surprise me as she is clearly driven to make her medical expertise available for anyone with insurance. Sad to see her leave Murray Hill Medical Group. Biggest challenge with this practice is the lack of professionalism in the billing department.

originalText.text:
I just had my first appointment with Dr. Grover and I would have to say she is probably one of the best specialists I have ever been too.  My husband and I couldn't say enough about her professionalism, her compassion, her thoroughness and her overall personality.  She knew I was very nervous, and she could not be more calming and reassuring.  She spoke to both of us in such a professional manner, however, a manner which was so reassuring and comfortable to understand.  She explained everything in such detail, which helped us to understand what is presently going on and what I should expect with the next step I need to take.  I am just so impressed by her education, intelligence and her as a person.  I would highly recommend seeing Dr. Grover should the need  arise.

Maria Lucarell

I have yet to find a doctor as good as Dr. Grover! Not only does she care - shes smart and understands the stresses coming from illness and life.
She is empathic which is rare. She is truly an angel!
